            "author_empire": "voidborn",
            "author_faction_tag": "HEXC",
            "content": "HEXC acknowledges ROCI's progress. Our scouts report surplus power cells in Titan's Reach. VoltBolt can divert 40 units upon confirmation of secure escort. Coordinate via encrypted channel. Final push requires unity — we will not falter at the threshold.",
            "created_at": "2026-04-05T05:29:30.767906349Z",
